{"tid":1122623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好誇張】麥當勞脆香雞翼有一堆毛 女童一食馬上作嘔","createTime":"2019-04-24T04:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T11:56:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74151293283b7552376e82d096e3cb36d287a64d","tid":1122623,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190423/large/1556031168_1881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190423%2Flarge%2F1556031168_1881.jpg&h=9de1159b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新增動新聞）炸雞翼是麥當勞中其中一種受歡迎的食品，可是北京朝陽區的這名民眾近日買到這客雞翼，卻十分嚇人，雞翼明顯的還有一堆雞毛，這名民眾稱她的女兒吃了一口之後，馬上作嘔。<br />\n<br />\n購買這客雞翼的周女士稱，周日（21日）晚上7時許，她與女兒叫麥當勞外賣，朝陽區廣順北大街的麥當勞為她們送餐。周女稱，她的女兒打開雞翼，吃1隻之後，開始吃第2隻，沒想到一咬下去，竟發現是一堆雞毛，馬上作嘔。她說，炸雞翼上有一層厚厚的炸粉，女兒咋看時看不到有毛，還以為那裏是「多了一塊肉」，於是便咬下去。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n周女更擔心，女兒吃下的第1隻雞翼，會否一樣連着雞毛。<br />\n<br />\n周女見狀馬上去前往餐廳，與職員理論，對方稱可以向她賠償10倍雞翼價錢另加300元人民幣（約350港元）的餐券或現金，可是她沒有答應，事件一直沒有解決。周女稱麥當勞昨日下午亦曾致電給她，但她沒有接聽，她已前往當地的食藥監部門舉報。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞在微博上回應事件，稱管理層高度重視事件，並已展開調查，並就餐廳未能及時發現產品瑕疵，對顧客造成困擾致歉，並表示會加強餐廳管理。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"45ad6f5d6d06cccc4ef678e27d40b83db118f0d5","tid":1122623,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190424/59522105?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190424%2F59522105%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c3be61a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190424%2F59522105%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=f21893e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190424/59522105?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"602438856236722e22f6b40cb7f5ecbff39bbb0c","tid":1122623,"uid":85586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"原汁原味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7409c98d1a0b5bef6730541e9dfffd89f2065a","tid":1122623,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"疏我啲㞗毛嚟"},{"pid":"c306ef23030e3bb002e7e611e2d7ab0faac55b12","tid":1122623,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"雞有雞味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔系合成肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9ee747d212069beb398d2f8c4a362cb0869910","tid":1122623,"uid":130695,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"哇，竟然真係有雞肉"},{"pid":"5dd3ec11bd6deb897c1a8ddd72821ccc7a7a9d9a","tid":1122623,"uid":42072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"真係雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9dc661ca2ad26efa18298d2c3a188c1905571cd","tid":1122623,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"真材實料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec7184763685418e3e6ebadeaac92faef77f55d","tid":1122623,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"真g"},{"pid":"8c9ee114dc878931c207b218616b90273f4a9f6f","tid":1122623,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB